Package: endid
Title: Engression-Based Distributional Difference-in-Differences
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Xiang", "Ao", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "xiangao@example.com")
Description: Combines Lee & Wooldridge (2025) panel DiD transformations with
    engression distributional regression to produce quantile treatment effects
    (QTE), conditional average treatment effects (CATE), and counterfactual
    distributions. Implements unit-specific residualization and uses engression
    for nonlinear distributional estimation. Supports both common-timing and
    staggered adoption designs with bootstrap inference.
